      "module_path": "chain",
      "docs": "Full contract for chains ①②③ that persist their computed signal documents. Provides `calc` (compute + persist), `load` (read persisted), `check_freshness` (stale detection), `evaluate_gate` (signal-gate logic delegating to domain pure functions), plus error-to-VerifyOutcome converters. The `SoTChain::check` blanket impl for any `T: PersistedSoTChain` runs `load → check_freshness → evaluate_gate`. Chain ⓪ does not implement this trait. Note: associated types Persisted/CalcError/StaleError are represented as placeholder Self in method signatures; catalogue schema cannot express associated types.",
